# Importação das Bibliotecas

import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import alpenglow as ag
from alpenglow.offline.models import FactorModel
from alpenglow.offline.evaluation import NdcgScore

import alpenglow
import alpenglow.experiments
import alpenglow.evaluation

# Dados de treinamaento

train_batch = pd.read_csv(
    'train_batch.csv',
    header=None,
    names=['time','user','item']
)

# Dados de teste

test_batch = pd.read_csv(
    'recsys-2017-tutorial/test_batch.csv',
    header=None,
    names=['time','user','item']
)

# Definização dos atributos do modelo

model = FactorModel(
    dimension=20,
    learning_rate=0.05,
    negative_rate=9,
    number_of_iterations=4,
)
model.fit(train_batch)

beginTime = 210006071959
day = 86400
year = day * 365
halfYear = (year + 1)/2

batch_mf_experiment = alpenglow.experiments.BatchFactorExperiment(
    negative_rate=19,
    period_length=halfYear,
    learning_rate=0.05,
    number_of_iterations=4,
)
batch_mf_ranks = batch_mf_experiment.run(train_batch, verbose=False)
